name: Feed The Cat! (glitch250)
description:
A game made for Mini Jam 105:

Controls:

WASD or arrow keys to move

Mouse to aim, Left Mouse Click to fire.

Made with Unity 2021.3.1f1

Audio made by me using:
https://www.beepbox.co
